textAfterTable: 12 Songs Biography Born: 05 August 1968 in Montreal, Quebec, Canada Genre: Country Years Active: '90s, '00s, '10s Like her contemporary Shania Twain, singer/songwriter Terri Clark came storming out of Canada and captured the attention of America's country music industry in the mid-'90s. Where Twain incorporated more rock & roll elements into her music, Clark largely stayed close to her country roots, even if those roots were more new country than hardcore honky tonk.
